                    <div class="meta">
                        <h3>Further Quotes From Srila Prabhupada Regarding Grhasta Asrama</h3>
                        <span class="date">
                            26 May 2018
                        </span>               
                    </div>
                </a>
            </header>
            <div class="body">Here are some quotes from Srila Prabhupada which, even extracted from His letters, are by no means circumstantial. Nothing what we see today was not present during the time Srila Prabhupada preached on this planet. There are no new problems, just the vocabulary may changed in deceiving way. Problems are the same and so are the solutions.


</div>
